{{lang|zh|sc=Hant|着}} is both the standard and variant traditional character of some senses of {{zh-l|*著}} (Pronunciations 1 and 2). Its usage varies with region:

{{Chinese-region variant characters|著|着}}

In mainland China's {{w|Table of General Standard Chinese Characters}} ({{w2|zh|通用规范汉字表}}), {{l|zh|著|tr=zhù}} is not listed as a traditional form of {{lang|zh|sc=Hans|着}} and is considered a separate character. <!-- Refer character 2198 (著) and 2398 (着) of https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/通用規范漢字表 -->
